Description: Very scary crossing Manurah Road close to giant roundabout near Mandgoorup entrance into Mandurah from the Freeway

Main risk: Poor road markings or no edge-lines
Description: The road has no reflectors and at night you cant see the road, the bridge is very narrow and there are no markers or reflectors on it at all, at night it is very dangerous and if it's raining part of the bridge turns into a big puddle and this is very dangerous.

Main risk: Vehicles travel over the speed limit
Description: Speed limit of 90km/h is too low for this road. Thomas Rd is 90km/h and has nowhere near the same infrastructure.
